【20220602回家作業, Bonus】

請計算玩兩場賭局與玩三場賭局的最佳比例，GHPR，與下面下注比例與資金成長的關係曲線。

plotBidding<-function(Bid,OptF,pwin,odds,nbet){
  plot(Bid,type='l',lwd=2,col="red",xlim=c(0,100), xlab="The Bidding fractoin(%)",ylab="The Growth Rate(%)",
       main=paste0("Bidding:",OptF,"%",", WinRate: ",pwin*100,"%, ","Odds: ",odds,", 40 Games"))
  #axis(1,seq(0,100,10))
  abline(h=1,lty=2,col="green")
  abline(v=order(Bid)[length(Bid)],lty=2,col="blue")
  points(x=OptF,y=max(Bid),col="black")
  text(x=OptF,y=max(Bid),round(max(Bid),4),pos=4,cex =1, pch = 3)
}

只玩1場40局,最佳下注比例25%,資金運用達25%！

nbet=40/1
GHPR1=NULL
for(f in seq(0,abs(1),0.01)){
  GHPR1=c(GHPR1,((1+f*odds)^(pwin*nbet)) * 
            ((1-f)^((1-pwin)*nbet))
          )
}
OptF=as.numeric(which(GHPR1==max(GHPR1)))-1
plotBidding(round(GHPR1,2),OptF,pwin,odds,nbet)

同時玩2場,每場各壓23%,資金運用達46%！

nbet=40/2
GHPR2=NULL
for(f in seq(0,abs(1/2),0.01)){
  GHPR2=c(GHPR2,
          (((1+f*odds+f*odds)^(pwin*nbet)) *  #WinWin
          ((1+f*odds+f*(-1))^(pwin*nbet))  *  #WinLose
          ((1+f*(-1)+f*odds)^(pwin*nbet))  *  #LoseWin
          ((1+f*(-1)+f*(-1))^(pwin*nbet))) #LoseLose
          )
}
OptF=as.numeric(which(GHPR2==max(GHPR2)))-1
plotBidding(round(GHPR2,2),OptF,pwin,odds,nbet)

同時玩3場,每場各壓21%,資金運用達63%！

nbet=10
GHPR3=NULL
for(f in seq(0,1/3,0.01)){
  GHPR3=c(GHPR3,
          (((1+f*odds+f*odds+f*odds)^(pwin*nbet)) *  #WinWinWin
           ((1+f*odds+f*odds+f*(-1))^(pwin*nbet)) *  #WinWinLose
           ((1+f*odds+f*(-1)+f*(-1))^(pwin*nbet)) *  #WinLoseLose
           ((1+f*odds+f*(-1)+f*odds)^(pwin*nbet)) *  #WinLoseWin
           ((1+f*(-1)+f*odds+f*odds)^(pwin*nbet)) *  #LoseWinWin
           ((1+f*(-1)+f*odds+f*(-1))^(pwin*nbet)) *  #LoseWinLose
           ((1+f*(-1)+f*(-1)+f*odds)^(pwin*nbet)) *  #LoseLoseWin
           ((1+f*(-1)+f*(-1)+f*(-1))^(pwin*nbet))    #LoseLoseLose
           )
        )
}
OptF=as.numeric(which(GHPR3==max(GHPR3)))-1
plotBidding(round(GHPR2,2),OptF,pwin,odds,nbet)
